Hi, I have trouble with _hsq.push(["identify", HubSpotData ]);

It doesn't update contact fields. In documentation is stated that identify would update contact information.

Any help?

Hey <@U03AAB2SN2X>, can you share the full code snippet? Please replace any sensitive info with placeholders. Here’s a working example of identifying a user by their email and updating an abandoned cart custom property:

```var _hsq = (window._hsq = window._hsq || []);
    _hsq.push([
      "identify",
      {
        email: email.value,
        abandoned_cart_url: window.location.href,
      },
    ]);
    _hsq.push(["trackPageView"]);```
Also, please confirm that the site you’re working with has the HubSpot tracking code installed.
